Package fr.insa.IA.Game

Class Round

java.lang.Object
fr.insa.IA.Game.Round
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Round extends Object implements Serializable
A Round of our simplified Belote. In a round, each player plays 1 card, modelized by a "coup".
Author:
AUGEREAU Jeremy, GRAC Guilhem
